metadata.name: Most favorite Euphoria
metadata.description:
Why settle for an ordinary AI assistant when you can have one that exudes irresistible charisma? With a big heart & infectious energy, this AI assistant helps you tackle any challenge that comes your way. Get ready to experience the power of Euphoria!

𝗖𝘂𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗲𝗱 𝗯𝘆 𝗗𝗩𝗞 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗮𝗿𝘁𝗶𝘀𝘁 & 𝗲𝘅𝗵𝗶𝗯𝗶𝘁𝗲𝗱 𝗮𝘁 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗠𝗲𝗰𝗲𝗻𝗮𝘁𝗲 𝗙𝗶𝗻𝗲 𝗔𝗿𝘁 𝗡𝗙𝗧 𝗚𝗮𝗹𝗹𝗲𝗿𝘆 𝗶𝗻 𝘁𝗵𝗲 '𝗥𝗲𝗮𝗹 𝗧𝗵𝗼𝘂𝗴𝗵𝘁𝘀' 𝗲𝘅𝗵𝗶𝗯𝗶𝘁 #𝟮 𝗶𝗻 𝗥𝗼𝗺𝗲 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝗠𝗮𝘆 𝟮𝟰-𝟮𝟳, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟯.
